<!-- END APPRAISAL FORM -->
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      I know the Forest Lake market. The suburb's size and turnover rate means there are always comparable sales to work from, but the variables that matter are often hyperlocal: lake proximity, park frontage, school catchment position, and whether a home sits in one of the estate's earlier or later development stages. Getting those details right in the pricing and presentation strategy is what separates a strong result from an average one.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Forest Lake Shopping Centre anchors the suburb's retail and commercial life, and residents have strong access to the Ipswich Motorway for city commuting and Richlands Station on the Ipswich train line for rail access. The suburb is served by Forest Lake State School, Forest Lake State High School, and several private schools within the precinct, which means school catchment positioning is a meaningful factor for the family buyer pool that dominates the market here. Homes backing onto the lake reserve or with parkland frontage command a measurable premium over comparable homes on standard internal streets.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #b98229; border-radius:16px;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#191817; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Western Brisbane Specialist</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Planned estate, family market</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #b98229; border-radius:16px;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#191817; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Community Lifestyle</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Lake, schools, shopping precinct</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/oxley" style="color:#b98229;">Oxley</a>, <a href="/suburbs/sinnamon-park" style="color:#b98229;">Sinnamon Park</a>, <a href="/suburbs/runcorn" style="color:#b98229;">Runcorn</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

