<section style="background:var(--color-base, #f2ead4); padding:40px 24px 80px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#b98229; margin-bottom:1rem;">FAQ</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:400; font-variation-settings:'opsz' 32; line-height:1.2; color:#191817; margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Common questions about Forest Lake.</h2>
    <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column;">

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What drives property values in Forest Lake?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Forest Lake values are shaped by proximity to the central lake, block size, and condition. Homes backing onto parkland or with lake views attract a premium. Family-sized blocks with multiple living zones are what the core buyer pool is seeking, and school catchment access remains a key consideration for buyers at the family end of the market.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          How long does it take to sell a home in Forest Lake?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Well-presented Forest Lake homes typically sell within 28 to 42 days. The suburb has a deep family buyer pool drawn by its schools, community infrastructure and relative affordability. Price accuracy is critical: buyers here are well-researched and understand the comparable sales data.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What is the lifestyle like in Forest Lake?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Forest Lake is designed as a self-contained community with its own shopping centre, schools, sporting clubs and the central lake reserve. Families choose it for the lifestyle completeness rather than proximity to the CBD. The lake walkway, parks and recreational facilities are what make the suburb distinctive in its price range.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          Is Forest Lake a good suburb to sell in?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Forest Lake generates consistent demand from families, particularly those relocating from higher-cost inner suburbs. The suburb's size means there is always an active buyer pool, and well-positioned homes attract genuine competition. Turnover rates are healthy relative to comparable outer-suburban estates.</p>
      </details>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

